  "markdown_content": "\n## 7d LIFE — Full Knowledge\n\n\n### Type\n\nProject — product/app specification\n\n\n### Working title\n\n7d LIFE — Flower Coaching App\n\n\n### Core concept\n\nThe app models life through 7 chakra petals, each representing a life domain.\n\n\n### Fixed 7-petal model\n\n1. Root — red — body, safety, money, home, routines\n1. Sacral — orange — emotions, pleasure, creativity, sensuality, play\n1. Solar Plexus — yellow — confidence, willpower, work, boundaries, power\n1. Heart — green — love, relationships, compassion, self-love\n1. Throat — blue — communication, truth, self-expression, honesty\n1. Third Eye — indigo — clarity, intuition, mindset, vision, focus\n1. Crown — violet — meaning, spirituality, purpose, alignment\n\n### Scoring logic\n\nPer-petal score: 0-10\n\nState labels:\n\n- 0-3: Crisis / Blocked\n- 4-5: Unstable / Wobbly\n- 6-7: Stable / Functional\n- 8-10: Thriving / Radiant\n\n### Derived metrics\n\n- 7D Life Score = average of last known scores\n- Balance Score = highest minus lowest score\n\n### Main flows\n\nOnboarding, Baseline Assessment, 90-Day Goal Setup, Dashboard, Petal Detail, Weekly Tracker, 90-Day Review\n\n\n### Technical direction\n\nReact + TypeScript, Tailwind, API backend, SQL persistence, modular architecture\n"
}